<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<head>
  <title>@kziel Suites Drink Request</title>
  <script>
  var drinks = <%= raw(@drinks.to_json) %>;
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="cheatline">
    <div class="title"><a href="http://twitter.com/kziel">@kziel</a> Suites Drink Request</div>
    <div class="blue"></div>
    <div class="gold"></div>
    <div class="yellow"></div>
    <div class="slant"></div>
    <div class="logo"></div>
    <div class="text">
      <span>I've got 21 hours in Singapore Suites and another 4 in Singapore First. Request a single drink and I'll drink the whole thing,</span><br> no matter how bad it is. And tweet you a photo #kzielsuitesdrink.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="info" style="height:auto;">
      <% Vote.all.each do |drink| %>
        <div>
          <%= "#{drink.twitter_name} - #{Drink.find(drink.drink_id).name}" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
